(Agentic Cyber Defense - Workflow Overview) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Main Flow:) Tj
T*
(Input Logs -> main.py -> Coordinator.run -> LogAgent -> AnalysisAgent) Tj
T*
(-> LLMExplanationAgent -> PolicyAgent -> ResponseAgent -> Final Output) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(1\) main.py) Tj
T*
(   - Loads input JSON logs, falls back to mock logs on error \(optional\).) Tj
T*
(   - Calls Coordinator.run\(logs, source\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(2\) LogAgent.collect) Tj
T*
(   - Normalizes logs to plain text lines.) Tj
T*
(   - Computes cloud metrics: service, error rate, source IP stats, request rate.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(3\) AnalysisAgent.analyze) Tj
T*
(   - DrainParser creates normalized templates and event IDs.) Tj
T*
(   - InferencePipeline computes model anomaly score via LSTM autoencoder.) Tj
T*
(   - Heuristic score checks attack-like patterns \(failed auth, flood, scan, exfil\).) Tj
T*
(   - Final anomaly score = max\(model_score, heuristic_score\).) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(4\) LLMExplanationAgent.explain) Tj
T*
(   - Builds a rule-based prior attack guess.) Tj
T*
(   - Prompts Gemini for JSON explanation and action recommendation.) Tj
T*
(   - If Gemini fails/unavailable, returns safe fallback explanation.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(5\) PolicyAgent.decide) Tj
T*
(   - Uses anomaly score + attack type to assign severity and actions.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(6\) ResponseAgent.respond) Tj
T*
(   - Converts allowed actions into human-readable operational responses.) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
(Final context keys:) Tj
T*
(source, raw_logs, cloud_metrics, parsed_events, event_sequence, templates,) Tj
T*
(analysis, llm_explanation, policy, response) Tj
